  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients hospitalized for ICH will be asked to provide their permission for the use of this
        information for retrospective research studies directed at ICH; such research to be
        conducted by the MNEMONICH investigators.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of spontaneous intracerebral hemorrhage (ICH) met by clinical and imaging
             criteria

          -  Age 18 and above

          -  Able to consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  ICH due to trauma

          -  ICH due to vascular malformation or aneurysm

          -  ICH due to brain tumor

          -  ICH due to underlying infectious lesion (e.g., abscess)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
